snippet: Jacob Tierney’s comedy focuses on a single, childless and irresponsible woman who pretends to be pregnant after a mistaken assumption.
abstract: Neil Genzlinger reviews movie Preggoland, directed by Jacob Tierney and starring Sonja Bennett.
